Identification of Singularity with "universal alignment" is not at all necessary. It's the point of phase-change. Very closely related to spontaneous order, which applies to profoundly unaligned multiplicities, such as wars and arms races, eco-systems, and markets.
... If anything, singularity is the real alternative to universal alignment. Catallactic coherence against planned unity.
